                    <br>When it comes to cooldowns, we have access to @Spell("Avenging Wrath"), @Spell("Divine Toll"), @Spell("Aura Mastery"), and @Spell("Beacon of Virtue"). I cover @Spell("Beacon of Virtue") in the advanced section, so be sure to check that out.
